SUMMARY:FROCIO: 80's Italo Disco
DESCRIPTION:March 14\, 2026  //  10pm // 19+\n$10 + fees\nBUY TICKETS \n \nWe’re on a ROLLLLLL baby because we have yet another NEW regular @buddies.nightlife event just for you… introducing FROCIO! \nAn 80’s Italo Disco party with sounds from the old end of the world! Think cheap drum machines with romantic analog synths elevated by the vocals of your favourite Italian diva singers. This is a world where sunny Campari spritzes existed on the beach with your linens\, tanning oil and sunglasses on next to your favourite local Sciura…. except really you’re just at the club. \nThis one goes out to my Italian ex-boyfriend who would’ve loved to attend but I banned him from Buddies.\nOh and in case you were wondering\, “Frocio” means f*g*ot in Italian. \nItalo disco | Hi-NRG | 80s Synth Pop | Euro Dance | Freestyle
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/frocio-80s-italo-disco/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
